{"tid":1671223,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗痾血尿","createTime":"2019-10-23T10:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T12:00:08.000Z","uid":55273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc48edfae04049a2de28b31bf9f76bdfc001b7c","tid":1671223,"uid":55273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"有無奴才既主子試過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一歲仔 食得瞓得玩得精神<br />\n但好奇怪 平時痾尿都係正常黃色<br />\n留意過 無飲得特別多或者少水<br />\n去痾尿既次數都正常<br />\n<br />\n但一帶佢去公園玩<br />\n玩得耐少少 <br />\n番到黎都會痾1,2次血尿 跟住又正常番<br />\n<br />\n上星期帶佢打針問過獸醫<br />\n然後佢話 係唔正常 但原因可以有好多<br />\n最好觀察下 再有就即刻驗尿 <br />\n唔知大家有無試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3fb46e122f708dd44391974ad55db0528bd7e2","tid":1671223,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rWyof9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rWyof9.gif&h=0c250780&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59bf0d5ab9003f23581dc83f729c1dbc2c48dde2","tid":1671223,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"D尿有無特別難聞"},{"pid":"87799c62452359699713b10b191716fe34842d24","tid":1671223,"uid":55273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59bf0d5ab9003f23581dc83f729c1dbc2c48dde2","tid":1671223,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"D尿有無特別難聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bace5e8de59a8b841e0eefcfc857fc73c14c1e6","tid":1671223,"uid":283431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"佢痾血尿嗰陣<br />\n有冇好痛苦咁？"},{"pid":"6c8458f02df3792242aa360a92bb11a302816b2c","tid":1671223,"uid":55273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2bace5e8de59a8b841e0eefcfc857fc73c14c1e6","tid":1671223,"uid":283431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"佢痾血尿嗰陣<br />\n有冇好痛苦咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"就係無囉奇怪<br />\n不過 佢每次去完玩番黎都會等好耐先痾<br />\n就會係好大篤尿同唔同色<br />\n<br />\n平時佢都係養生撚 早午晚痾屎尿都好規律下 <br />\n又中意飲水<br />\n每次都係去玩耐少少(1個鐘左右)就會痾1,2篤<br />\n<br />\n攝於上次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQMuLVz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQMuLVz.png&h=1738a1d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a0d83fbc9804f310d7643aec3bc090896187e49","tid":1671223,"uid":184234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:20:51.000Z","msg":"狗狗中暑都會痾血尿"},{"pid":"162f60547946861c5a56823bbf431bbdc21a6398","tid":1671223,"uid":55273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a0d83fbc9804f310d7643aec3bc090896187e49","tid":1671223,"uid":184234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:20:51.000Z","msg":"狗狗中暑都會痾血尿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"呢個機會微啲<br />\n玩都有keep住比佢飲水同埋<br />\n唔會咁岩每次去玩完都一定中暑咁岩掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c4cd5a9fc38951160437a8edd435721f1aae05","tid":1671223,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"以前隻8哥柯尿有血<br />\n之後睇係腎有問題"},{"pid":"e17320d5c33492daedefc8832e6f03d79aab4db4","tid":1671223,"uid":55273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c4cd5a9fc38951160437a8edd435721f1aae05","tid":1671223,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"以前隻8哥柯尿有血<br />\n之後睇係腎有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"然後點呀？無事？<br />\n我只係好奇怪點解每次都係玩完就有<br />\n係屋企既話又無事姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}